  "name": "Horrific Appearance",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/green_12.jpg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>All qlippoth have such horrific and mind-rending shapes that those who gaze upon them suffer all manner of ill effects. A qlippoth can present itself as a standard action to assault the senses of all living creatures within 30 feet. The exact effects caused by a qlippoth&rsquo;s horrific appearance vary by the type of qlippoth. A successful Will save (DC 10 + 1/2 the qlippoth&rsquo;s Hit Dice+ the qlippoth&rsquo;s Charisma modifier): reduces or negates the effect.</p>\n<p>This ability is a mind-affecting <a class=\"entity-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; background-image: none; background-color: initial; padding: 0px; color: #ff6400; border: none;\" draggable=\"false\" data-pack=\"pf-content.pf-universal-monster-rules\" data-id=\"QAVtt2JtZwWPVk4j\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; text-decoration-line: underline;\">Gaze</span></a> attack.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em>Location:&nbsp;</em>Special Abilities</p>\n<p><em>Usage:</em> Effect varies by Qlippoth, replace context notes.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
